headline: Accenture to acquire Cabel Industry, terms not disclosed
summary: Accenture (ACN) has entered into an agreement with the Fibonacci Group to acquire Cabel Industry, an Italian technology company that provides specialized core banking and IT managed services to mid-size financial institutions. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed. Completion of the acquisition is subject to customary closing conditions.
